{
  "stem": "26731.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I liked it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he was outvoted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what happened with the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was told afterwards that he was quite against it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my father one time went down one of the main thoroughfares in Berlin and passed a bank, with a young lady trying to get the marquee up and down, it was stuck.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He helped her, let me help you, and that's the way they met.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excellent, that's correct.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know that, of course, some eyebrows were raised for the families, but only temporarily.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I must--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course, usually marrying a Jewish person-- not to be ultra anti-Semitic, but even there, Protestant married Protestant, Catholic married Catholics, and Jews married Jews.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's the order there?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was Protestant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lutheran, what they call in Germany they have it either Catholic or Evangelical, Evangelisch, that's what they call it, but in effect it's Lutheran.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course I was told I guess my father's side, particularly Aunt Bertha who was my father's aunt, Was somewhat surprised too, but after she met my mother she was accepted.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was actually yes, one of my father's cousin, not many relatives left, but she was, Aunt Bertha, yes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Baumgard. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, I was being told when I was born one uncle had to go out, get a big cab, to she was very particular, didn't like to go by car, the biggest cab, and she rode down to the hospital to visit my mother.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the other side, of course, even if eyebrows were raised, my father was a judge.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was quite-- at that time a judge was a very good position and therefore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the way I understand the eyebrow raising was only temporary, and everything worked out.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
